<div class="home-page" style="background-color: black;">
  <header>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <%= video_tag "dj_vid.mp4", autoplay: :autoplay, loop: :loop, muted: :muted %>
    <div class="container h-100">
      <div class="d-flex h-100 text-center align-items-center">
        <div class="w-100 text-white">
          <h1 class="display-3">Bite Jockey</h1>
          <h3 class="lead mb-0">Less Admin More Mixin</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg" id="home-buttons"><%= link_to 'Sort Ya Tracks', '/auth/spotify', method: :post %></button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg m-3" id="home-buttons"><%= link_to 'Get A Bit Social', 'social', method: :post %></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="container-md" id="api-features" style="text-align: center; padding: 0;">
    <h1>How Bite Jockey Can Raise Your DJ Game</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Access Your Own Spotify Playlists</h3>
          <p class="card-text">We'll link up your existing Spotify playlists so you can work on those #{DJ-Adjective} sets you've already made, instead of starting from scratch.</p>
          <%= image_tag 'playlists.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">BiteJockey's Intelligent Sort</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Let BiteJockey's Intelligent Algorithm automatically sort your playlist which is guaranteed to generate a killer set playlist.</p>
          <%= image_tag 'sort.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Custom Sort By DJ Specific Filters</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Choose to manually filter your existing playlists based on unique DJ-relevant categories such as BPM, Key, Danceability, Energy and plenty more. </p>
          <%= image_tag 'filter3.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Save or Create Playlists</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Once the magic's been worked you can remove songs that don't fit, save the final result as a new playlist or over-ride the original playlist.</p>
          <%= image_tag 'save.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="glow-on-hover" type="button" style="font-size: x-large;">Get Started</button>
  </div>
  <div class="banner" id="social-banner" >
    <div class="container h-100">
      <div class="d-flex h-100 text-center align-items-center">
        <div class="w-100 text-white">
          <h1 class="display-3">Bite Social</h1>
          <h3 class="lead mb-0">A Space for Music Lovers and DJs to Collaborate, Share and Get Booked.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="arrow-container animated fadeInDown">
          <div class="arrow-2">
            <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow-1 animated hinge infinite zoomIn"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-md" id="api-features" style="text-align: center; padding: 0;">
    <h1>The Social Space for Music Creators, Fans and Venues.</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Make A Profile That's All You</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Have fun being you. Share what you love, your unique sounds and style and show off those deadly playlists!</p>
          <%= image_tag 'profile.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Open, Inclusive, BS-Free</h3>
          <p class="card-text">We'll leave the toxicity to the other social sites. Bite Social is all for friends, sharing cool stuff, positive vibes, encouragement and inclusivity.</p>
          <%= image_tag 'smile.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Connect With Other DJs</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Choose to manually filter your existing playlists based on unique DJ-relevant categories such as BPM, Key, Danceability, Energy and plenty more. </p>
          <%= image_tag 'multi.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6" id="api-card-feature">
          <h3 class="card-title">Get Booked or Book DJs</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Once the magic's been worked you can remove songs that don't fit, save the final result as a new playlist or over-ride the original playlist.</p>
          <%= image_tag 'booked.jpg', width: '100%', height: '60%'%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="glow-on-hover" type="button" style="font-size: x-large; margin-bottom: 80px;">Get Social</button>
  </div>

</div>
